  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Coffee Barista - Tiong Bahru bakery",
  "description": "<p><strong>Coffee Baristas for Hire! - Brew the freshest cup of Coffee with us at Tiong Bahru Bakery 2.0!</strong><br /><br /><strong>Pour the Freshest Cup of Cappuccino with our Latest Concept!</strong><br />✨ Love coffee as much as we do? Tiong Bahru Bakery is in the midst of transitioning to get a bold new look — and we need baristas who can bring the same energy behind the bar! Be part of the Tiong Bahru Bakery Front of House Team and show off your skills in pulling the perfect espresso, crafting latte art, and serving up good vibes with every cup! ☕ <br /><br /><em><strong>No Experience? Don't sweat it! - we’ll provide hands-on training to help you grow into a skilled barista!</strong></em></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong><br />We are seeking enthusiastic and dedicated Baristas to join our team. As a Barista, you will play a vital role in crafting exceptional coffee beverages and providing outstanding customer service. This is an exciting opportunity for coffee lovers who are passionate about delivering a delightful experience to our guests.</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Learn the art of brewing — from pulling espresso shots to steaming milk and crafting latte art</li><li>Deliver warm and attentive service to every guest, ensuring their experience is as enjoyable as their coffee</li><li>Maintain a clean, organized, and welcoming coffee bar and café space</li><li>Work as part of a dynamic team, supporting one another during busy shifts</li><li>Follow food safety and hygiene standards in daily operations</li><li>Stay curious and open to learning!</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>44 hour 5 day work week</li><li>Comfortable to work on weekends and public holidays when required to</li><li>Basic understanding and experience in specialty coffee would be highly advantageous</li></ul><p><strong>Remuneration Structure</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $2,500 Completion Bonus (Terms and Conditions Applied)</li><li>End-year performance bonus</li><li>Medical and Dental Insurance Coverage</li><li>Meal Allowance provided</li><li>Team member Referral Bonuses</li><li>Great annual leave</li></ul>",
